definitions.definition: A special ward of Tokyo prefecture , Japan that is surrounded by the (clockwise from north) Toshima , Bunkyō , Chiyoda , Minato , Shibuya , and Nakano special wards; it is also the location of the Tokyo Metropolitan Government Office.
